                What We Believe
            </div>
            <div class="what-we-belive-content-body hidden">
                Jesus Christ is the Son of the Living God and the only Saviour from sin.<br />
                Jesus Christ is the Healer of the body through the shed Blood of Jesus Christ.<br />
