                    </div>
                    <div class="vision-content-title">
                        3. The Local Church
                    </div>
                    <div class="vision-content-body">
                        God’s will is accomplished in us and through us as we connect and commit ourselves to a local church.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Vision 4 -->
            <div class="main-visions hidden">
                <div class="vision-content">
                    <div>
                        <img src="~/images/church vision image 4.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="vision-content-title">
