                    </div>
                    <div class="vision-content-body">
                        The highest calling of a Pastor and church is to obey God’s calling to make disciples in all the nations
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Vision 5 -->
            <div class="main-visions hidden">
                <div class="vision-content">
                    <div>
                        <img src="~/images/church vision image 5.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="vision-content-title">
                        5. Church Planting
                    </div>
                    <div class="vision-content-body">
                        Disciples are raised up so that they can be released into surrounding cities and countries to reproduce our vision.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Vision 6 -->
            <div class="main-visions hidden">
                <div class="vision-content">
                    <div>
                        <img src="~/images/church vision image 6.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="vision-content-title">
